### Source Summary

Civis is a **large, active, self-contained Rust monorepo** with 780+ commits, 616+ remote branches, 33+ workspace crates (`civ-inference`, `civ-protocol`, `civ-server`, `civ-codex`, `civ-client`, `civ-engine`, `civ-holocron`, `civ-bridge`, `civ-godtools`, `civ-infra`, etc.). It is an emergent civilization simulation built with Bevy 0.15, described as "8/10 complete, 82.6% coverage, playable voxel build shipped."

The repo has 272+ governance/markdown documents (ADRs, PRD, PLAN, charter, SPEC, SOTA, worklogs). It is the **canonical home** for the Civis project — not a candidate for deletion or absorption.

